          "bug_bounty_scope": "in-scope",
          "notes": "An attacker can submit a blob via P2P containing byte sequences that encode values >= BLS_MODULUS. If bytes_to_bls_field silently wraps around, different client implementations may produce different field elements from the same blob, causing consensus divergence."
